182	/**
183	 * Poll until the target writ reaches a terminal-classification state.
184	 * Throws on timeout. Each poll shells out `nsg --guild-root <test-guild>
185	 * writ-show --id <writId> --format json`.
186	 *
187	 * Exposed as a standalone helper so both engines (the post-and-wait
188	 * happy path, and the standalone wait engine) share its behavior.
